                        <title xml:lang="he">קבץ לקוטים </title>
								
                        
                        
                        
                        <note>
									
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Contains, among others, the Commentary on the Torah by
                                        Abraham ibn Ezra (Exodus 3:13-3:14), various derashot, a
                                        treatise on the cycle of shemiṭot, a fragment of Sefer
                                        ha-Kanah, kabbalistic novellae on Talmud and midrashim,
                                        various kabbalistic notes quoting e.g. Isaac of Acre, and a
                                        treatise entitled Migdal ῾Oz (folio 11r).</p>
								
                        
                        
                        
                        </note>
							
                     
                     
                     
